<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="141" type="notes">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="141">Note.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="141">
This is the first report of this genus in Nepal. The genus 
<taxonomicName class="Liliopsida" family="Cyperaceae" genus="Machaerina" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Machaerina" order="Poales" pageId="0" pageNumber="141" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="141">Machaerina</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
shows morphological similarities to the genera 
<taxonomicName class="Liliopsida" family="Cyperaceae" genus="Cladium" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Cladium" order="Poales" pageId="0" pageNumber="141" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="141">Cladium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName class="Liliopsida" family="Cyperaceae" genus="Rhynchospora" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Rhynchospora" order="Poales" pageId="0" pageNumber="141" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="141">Rhynchospora</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. 
<taxonomicName class="Liliopsida" family="Cyperaceae" genus="Cladium" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Cladium" order="Poales" pageId="0" pageNumber="141" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="141">Cladium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is differentiated by its solid stem and ellipsoid achene lacking disc. 
<taxonomicName class="Liliopsida" family="Cyperaceae" genus="Machaerina" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Machaerina" order="Poales" pageId="0" pageNumber="141" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="141">Machaerina</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is differentiated from 
<taxonomicName class="Liliopsida" family="Cyperaceae" genus="Rhynchospora" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Rhynchospora" order="Poales" pageId="0" pageNumber="141" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="141">Rhynchospora</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by its leaf characters; the leaves in 
<taxonomicName class="Liliopsida" family="Cyperaceae" genus="Machaerina" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Machaerina" order="Poales" pageId="0" pageNumber="141" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="141">Machaerina</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
are distichously arranged, whereas in 
<taxonomicName class="Liliopsida" family="Cyperaceae" genus="Rhynchospora" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Rhynchospora" order="Poales" pageId="0" pageNumber="141" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="141">Rhynchospora</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, they are tristichously arranged.
</paragraph>
